column6: Natasha Romanoff's search for the truth behind the Icepick Protocols has taken her around the globe-and now she rockets straight into outer space! It's over the top action all the way-featuring the other Black Widow and two Captain Americas-as Marvel's deadliest beauty finally uncovers which part of her past has come back to bite her! Rated T  ...$3.99
